snippet.title: Slime Rancher - Viktor's Experimental Update is HERE!
snippet.description:
Join Viktor Humphries and test his simulated reality of the Far, Far Range. Well, a work-in-progress version anyway...

Download Viktor's Experimental Update for PC today! (Console update will be available shortly after)

Plus, check out the Secret Style Pack, an all-new downloadable content pack that re-styles every slime in Slime Rancher! Learn more here: http://slimerancher.com/SecretStyle



Follow us to stay up to date on news and events!

http://www.twitter.com/monomipark
http://www.instagram.com/monomi_park
http://www.blog.monomipark.com
